# AI Strategy Generator API Keys
# These are optional - only needed if you want to use the AI-powered strategy assistant

# OpenAI API Key
# Get yours at: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# Anthropic API Key
# Get yours at: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Notes:
# - API keys are stored in browser sessionStorage when entered in the UI
# - Keys are NOT persisted across browser sessions for security
# - You do not need to set these environment variables - the UI will prompt for them
# - This file is just for reference
